      • getAllQuestionsWithAnswers

        Question[] getAllQuestionsWithAnswers(AnswerSet as)
        This takes in an AnswerSet and returns all Questions, retired or not.

      • getQuestion

        Question getQuestion(java.lang.String questionID)

      • getOrderedQuestions

        Question[] getOrderedQuestions()
        Returns the questions ordered first according to priority and then according to public id. This method will sort the questions each and every time they are pulled, so if you are worried about performance use the method QuestionSet.getQuestions() instead.
        Returns:
        The questions in this question set ordered by priority and public id.

      • isQuestionSetAvailable

        boolean isQuestionSetAvailable(AnswerContainer answerContainer)
        Returns true if at least one of the questions in this set is visible based on the AnswerContainer.
